headline: Nvidia, Goldman Among Best Dow Stocks In June; Why July Could Be Golden
summary: Goldman Sachs, Nike and Nvidia were the best Dow stocks in June, leading the Dow Jones Industrial Average to its 4.3% gain for the month.  Goldman stock climbed nearly 18% in June, the best performance among the 30 Dow components.  The stock had to dig itself out of a 35% hole from February to early April, when President Donald Trump paused most tariffs and the stock market rebounded.
